hadiths[17]{hadithnumber,text}:
3624,"Hazrat Amr bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni wafat key waqt na koi dirham chhoda na deenar, na ghulam na londi, albatta aapka safed khachar jis par aap sawari farmaya kartey they. aap ka aslaha aur aap ki zamin tarkey mein shamil they magar aap ney unhen fi sabililah waqf farma diya tha. Quteba bin Saeed dusri martaba bator sadqa key alfaz bayan kartey hain."
3625,"Hazrat Amr bin Haris bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni wafat key waqt koi chiz chhod kar nahin gaey, ilawa aap key safed khachar, aslaha aur zamin key jinhen aap ney waqf qarar dey diya tha."
3626,"Hazrat Amr bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney (apni wafat key waqt ) apney khachar, aslaha aur zamin key ilawa kuch tarka nahin chhoda aur unhen bhi aap (apni zindagi mein) sadqa o waqf qarar dey chukey they. (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam)"
3627,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey khaibar key ilaqey mein kuch zamin mili. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : mujhey aisi zamin mili hai ke merey khayal key mutabiq mujhey us jaisi mehbub aur qeemti chiz kabhi nahin mili. (aur main chahta hun ke usey sadqa kar dun.) aap ney farmaya : agar to chahey to usey (waqf ki surat mein) sadqa kar dey. chunanche Hazrat umr ney wo zamin sadqa kar di, is shart par ke wo zamin na bechi ja sakegi, na kisi ko hiba ki jaeygi, albatta (us ki aamdani) fuqara, rishtedaaron, ghulamon (ki azadi), mehmano aur musafiron par kharch ki jaeygi. jo shakhs us zamin ka intizam kerega, uskey liye ijazat hai ke us sey munasib andaz mein kha pi ley aur apney milney jalney walon ko khula pila dey, albatta wo maal jama na kerey."
3628,(eik dusrey tareeq sey marwi riwayat mein) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey sabiqa riwayat ki tarah naqal farmatey hain.
3629,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaibar mein kuch zamin mili. wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur kaha : mainey aisi zamin hasil ki hai ke merey khayal key mutabiq us sey qeemti aur umda maal mujhey kabhi nahin mila. (mera khayal hai ke main usey sadqa kar dun) aap is barey mein kya hukm farmatey hain? aap ney farmaya : agar tum chaho to asal zamin ko waqf kar do aur uski aamdani sadqa kar do. chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney us shart par usey sadqa ( waqf ) kar diya ke usey na to bechaa ja sakega, na kisi ko hiba ki ja sakegi aur na is mein virasat chalegi, albatta uski aamdani fuqara, rishtedaaron, ghulamon ( ki azadi ), mujahideen, mehmano aur musafiron par kharch hogi. jo shakhs uska ناظم baneyga, wo munasib miqdaar mein us sey khud bhi kha pi sakta hai aur apney doston ko bhi khila pila sakta hai lekin wo us sey maal jama na kerey."
3630,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaibar mein zamin mili. wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur aap sey us silsiley mein mashwara kya aur kaha ke mujhey bahut qeemti aur lambi chodi zamin mili hai. mera khayal hai us sey qabl mujhey kabhi us sey qeemti aur umda maal nahin mila. aap kya hukm farmatey hain? aap ney farmaya : agar tum chaho to asal zamin ko waqf kar do aur uski aamdani sadqa kar do. chunanche unhoney zamin ko is tarah sadqa kar diya ke usey becha na ja sakega, na wo tohfey mein di ja sakegi. aur uski aamdani fuqara, rishtedaaron, ghulamon ( ki azadi ), mujahideen , musafiron aur mehmano par sadqa kar di. jo shakhs us ka intizam karey to uskey liye koi gunah nahin ke wo khud ( maroof tareeqey key mutabiq ) us sey kuch kha pi ley ya apney kisi dost ko khula pila dey, albatta maal jama na kerey. alfaz Ismail ( bin Masood ) key hain."
3631,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaibar key ilaqey mein kuch zamin hasil hui. wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas is silsiley mein mashwara karney key liye hazir huye to aap ney farmaya : agar tum chaho to asal zamin ko waqf kar do aur manaafey sadqa kar do. chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney asal zamin waqf kar di ke na usey bechaa jaey na hiba kya jaey, na is mein virasat jari ho. aur uski aamdani fuqaraa , rishtedaron , ghulamon , miskinon, musafiron aur mehmano key liye sadqa kar di. jo shakhs uska intizam kerey. uskey liye koi harj nahin ke khud maroof tareeqey key mutabiq us sey kha pi ley ya apney kisi dost ko khila pila dey, b-sharte-ke wo maal jama na kerey."
3632,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab ye aayat utri : « { لَنْ تَنَالُو الْبِرَّ حَتّٰی تُنْفِقُوا مِمَّا تُحِبُّونَ }  tum hergiz neki hasil na kar sakogey yahan tak ke wo chiz kharch karo jisey tum bahut pasand kartey ho. Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hamara rab taala hum sey hamarey maal talab farmata hai. aey Allah key Rasool ! main aap ko gawah banata hun ke mainey apni zamin Allah Taala ki raza mandi hasil karney key liye waqf kar di hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum usey apney rishtey daaron Hassan bin Sabit aur abi Kaab mein taqseem kar do.
3633,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha ke wo so hissey jo mujhey khaibar mein miley hain, mainey kabhi bhi un sey ziyada umda maal hasil nahin kya. mera irada hai ke wo sadqa kar dun. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : asal zamin waqf kar do aur uskey phal aur faslen sadqa kar do."
3634,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey aisa maal hasil huwa hai ke us jaisa kabhi hasil nahin huwa. merey paas so ghulam they. mainey unkey iwaz khaibar key ilaqey mein so hissey zamin kharid li. mera khayal hai ke main usey sadqa kar key Allah Taala ka qurb hasil karun. aap ney farmaya : asal zamin waqf kar do aur phal sadqa kar do.
3635,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey Samagh maqam par apni zamin key barey mein mashwara kya to aap ney farmaya : asal zamin waqf kar do aur us ka phal sadqa kar do."
3636,"Hazrat Husain bin Abdur-Rehman sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Amr bin Jaawaan sey, jo ke banu Tameem mein sey they, puchha ke Hazrat Ahnaf bin Qais (Saiyednaa Ali aur Muawiya Raziallahu anhuma ki kashmakash sey) alehda kyon rahey? wo kehney lagey : mainey Hazrat Ahnaf ko farmatey suna ke main eik dafa Haj ko jatey huye Madina Munawra gaya. abhi hum apney khemon mein apney paalaan hi utaar rahey they ke kisi aaney waley ney aa kar kaha : log masjid mein ikhattey ho chukey hain. mainey ja kar dekha to waqaee log jama they aur unkey darmiyan kuchh log bethey they. dekha to wo Ali bin Abi Talib , Zuber , Talha aur Saad bin Abi Waqas Raziallahu anhum they. jab main unkey paas khada tha to aawaz aai : ye Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) aagey hain. wo tashrif laye to un par eik badi si zard chadar thi. mainey apney sathi sey kaha : zara thehro taake main dekhun, aap kaisey tashrif laye hain? Hazrat Usman farmaney lagey : kya yahan Ali hain? Zuber hain? Talha hain? Saad hain? unhoney kaha : haan ! aap ney farmaya : main tumhen us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jo shakhs falan khandan ka khajuron ka baada kharid kar (masjid mein shamil kar) dega , Allah Taala uski maghfirat farma dega. mainey wo baada kharid kar diya, phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya ke mainey falan khandan ka baada kharid liya hai. aap ney farmaya : usey hamari masjid mein shamil kar do. us ka sawab tujhey milega? sab ney kaha : bilkul durust hai. aap ney farmaya : main tumhen uski qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jo shakhs rooma kunwaan khareedega , Allah Taala uski maghfirat farmaeyga. main (usey kharid kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : mainey rooma ka kunwaan kharid liya hai. aap ney farmaya : usey musalmanon key peeney key liye waqf kar do. us ka sawab tumhen zarur milega? sab ney kaha : bilkul theek hai. aap ney farmaya : main tumhen us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jo shakhs tangi waley lashkar ko tayyar kerega, Allah Taala uski maghfirat farmaeyga. mainey unhen sara saman diya yahan tak ke wo koi rassi ya mahaar (nakel) tak ki kami mehsus na kartey they? un sab ney kaha : bilkul sahih hai. Hazrat Usman kehney lagey : aey Allah ! gawah ho ja. aey Allah ! gawah ho ja ! aey Allah ! gawah ho ja !"
3637,"Hazrat Ahnaf bin Qais sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum (apney gharon sey) Haj karney key iraday sey nikley to Madina Munawra bhi gaey. abhi hum apni qiyam gaahon mein apney paalaan utaar hi rahey they ke kisi ney aa kar kaha : Masjide-Nabwi mein bahut sey log jama hain aur wo kuchh ghabraey huye sey hain. hum sab masjid ki taraf chaley to haqiqat mein log masjid key darmiyan mein chand buzurgon key ird-gird jama they. pata chala ke wo Ali , Zuber , Talha aur Saad bin Abi Waqas Raziallahu anhum hain. abhi hum isi tarah khadey they ke (Ameerul-Momeneen) Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) bhi tashrif ley aaye. un par zard rang ki eik badi chadar thi jis sey unhoney apney sar ko dhanp rakha tha. wo farmaney lagey : yahan Ali hain? Talha hain? Zuber hain? Saad hain? wo kehney lagey : ji haan. farmaney lagey : main tumhen us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jo shakhs falan khandan ka khaliyiaan khareedega , Allah Taala uski maghfirat farmaeyga. mainey bees ya pachchees hazar (dirham) ka kharida, phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur aap ko ittilaa ki. aap ney farmaya : is jagah ko hamari masjid mein shamil kar do. tumhen is ka sawab zarur milega? wo sab kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! sahih hai. phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : main tumhen us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jo shakhs biare-rooma khareedega , Allah Taala uski maghfirat farmaeyga. mainey wo kunwaan itni itni raqam sey kharida, phir mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya ke mainey wo kunwaan itney ka kharid liya hai. aap ney farmaya : usey aam musalmanon key peeney key liye waqf kar do. is ka sawab tumhen zarur milega? sab ney (tasdeeq kartey huye) kaha : Allah ki qism ! durust hai. phir kehney lagey : main tumhen us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon key chehron ko dekh kar farmaya tha : jo shakhs in (logon, yani tangi waley lashkar, mujahideen tabuk) ko saman mohaiyya kerega, Allah Taala uski maghfirat farmaeyga. mainey un sab ko saman mohaiyya kiya yahan tak ke unhen kisi rassi ya mahaar (nakel) ki bhi kami mehsus na hui? un sab ney kaha : han, Allah ki qism ! aap (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! to gawah ho ja. aey Allah ! to gawah ho ja. aey Allah ! to gawah ho ja."
3638,"Hazrat Samaama bin Huzn Qusheri sey manqul hai ke main us waqt Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar key paas mojud tha jab Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney deewar key ooper sey (muhaasra (gheraaw) karney waley baaghiyon par) jhaankaa aur farmaney lagey : main tum sey Allah ki qism aur Islam ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra tashrif laye to biare-rooma key siwa wahan mitha pani nahin tha. aap ney farmaya : koi shakhs biare-rooma kharid kar apna dol bhi dusrey musalmanon key dolon key barabar qarar dega to usey Allah Taala jannat mein is sey behtar ata farmaeyga. mainey apney khalis maal sey wo kunwaan kharid aur mainey is mein apney dol ko aam musalmanon key dolon key barabar hi samjha, jabkey aaj tum ney mujhey us sey pani peeney sey rok rakha hai yahan tak ke main samandari pani (jaisa namkeen pani) peeta hun? haazirin ney kaha : han, Allah ki qism ! (ye baat sahih hai). Hazrat Usman ney farmaya : main tum sey Allah ki qism aur Islam ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun ! kya tum jantey ho ke mainey (ghazwae-tabuk ka) tangi wala lashkar apney maal sey tayyar kiya tha? unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! haan. phir farmaya : main tum sey Allah ki qism aur Islam ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun, kya tum jantey ho ke Masjide-Nabwi namaaziyon key liye tang ho gaee thi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs falan khandan ka ehata kharid kar masjid mein izafa kerega to Allah Taala usey jannat mein is sey behtar dega. mainey apney khalis maal sey wo ehata kharid aur masjid mein izafa kar diya. aaj tum ney mujhey us masjid mein do rakat padhney sey rok rakha hai? haazirin ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! aap sahih keh rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : main tum sey Allah ki qism aur Islam ka wasta dey kar poochhta hun, kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama key sabeer pahad par they. aap key sath hazraat Abu-Bakar aur umr aur main bhi tha. pahad mein harkat hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is par apna paaun maara aur farmaya : aey sabeer ! sukoon sey reh. tujh par is waqt eik Nabi, eik Siddiq aur do shaheed hain? haaziriin ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! sach hai. aap ney na'rae takbir buland farmaya aur kaha : Kaba ke Rab ki qism ! un logon (merey makhalfeen) ney merey haq mein gawahi dey di, unhoney merey haq mein gawahi di hai ke main shaheed hunga."
3639,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman sey riwayat hai ke jab baaghiyon ney Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) (key ghar) ka muhaasra (ghairaaw) kar liya aur unhen (bahir nikalney sey rok diya) to aap ney eik dafa deewar key ooper sey unhen jhaankaa aur farmaya : main us shakhs sey gawahi ka mutalba karta hun jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pahad waley din jab us ney harkat ki thi aur aap ney is par apna paaun maara tha, ye farmatey suna hai ke aey pahad ! sukoon sey reh. (is waqt) tujh par Nabi, Siddiq aur do shaheedon key ilawa koi nahin. us waqt main bhi aap key sath tha. bahut sey haazirin ney iski gawahi di. phir Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main Allah ki qism dey kar us shakhs sey gawahi ka mutalba karta hun jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko baiatul-Rizwaan key din farmatey suna hai : ye Allah ka haath hai. aur ye Usman ka. bahut sey logon ney iski bhi gawahi di, phir farmaney lagey : main Allah ki qism dey kar us shakhs sey gawahi ka mutalba karta hun jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko tangi waley lashkar key din ye farmatey suna hai : aaj kon shakhs kharch kerega jo yaqinan qubul hoga? to mainey apney maal sey nisf (aadhe) lashkar ko saaz aur saman mohaiyya kya. is baat ki bhi bahut sey logon ney gawahi di, phir Hazrat Usman ney farmaya : main Allah ki qism deta hun us shakhs ko jisney suna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey, aap farmatey they : kon shakhs hai aisa jo badha dey is masjid (Nabawi) ko jannat key ghar key badley mein? phir mainey us zamin ko apney maal sey kharid liya. chunanche un logon ney uski bhi gawahi di, phir farmaya : main Allah ki qism dey kar us shakhs sey gawahi ka mutalba karta hun jisney biare-rooma ki farokht ka waqia dekha hai. mainey usey apney maal sey kharid kar musafiron key liye waqf kiya. bahut sey logon ney uski gawahi di."
3640,"Hazrat Abu-Abdur-Rehman Sulami sey riwayat hai ke jab Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko unkey ghar mein ghair liya gaya to log unkey ghar key bahar jama ho gaey. aap ney deewar sey un ki taraf sey jhaankaa. (phir raawi ney sabiqa (pichhli) hadees bayan ki) (tafsil key liye dekhiye, hadees : 3184)."
